    •	GET /api/name
    •	Dockerfile
    •	Jenkinsfile
    •	Deployment instructions
    •	Nginx reverse proxy

Backend
• Build Express API
• Add Dockerfile
• Push to Git
• Jenkins pipeline → builds + pushes Docker image
• Deploy on VM
• Nginx + HTTPS at api.yourdomain.com

Frontend (Next.js)
• Create Next.js app
• Implement “Welcome” UI
• Fetch backend API
• Add Dockerfile
• Jenkins pipeline
• Deploy to VM
• Nginx + HTTPS at yourdomain.com

Mobile
• Build React Native app
• Hit backend API
• Build release versions (.aab / .ipa)
• Publish to Play Store + App Store
